<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-6238] LOCAL_ONE doesn&apos;t work for SimpleStrategy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6238</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;LOCAL_ONE only works for NetworkTopologyStrategy which has DC specification. Any other strategy fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If there is no  DC specified in the strategy, we should treat LOCAL_ONE as ONE&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
